de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.evaluation.scores.adapter

Class OutlierScoreAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.evaluation.scores.adapter.OutlierScoreAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DBIDRefIter, ScoreEvaluation.ScoreIter, Iter

    public class OutlierScoreAdapter
extends Object
implements ScoreEvaluation.ScoreIter, DBIDRefIter
    This adapter can be used for an arbitrary collection of Integers, and uses that id1.compareTo(id2) != 0 for id1 != id2 to satisfy the comparability. Note that of course, no id should occur more than once. The ROC values would be incorrect then anyway!
    Since:
    0.7.0
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
